      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear including minor dents, scratches, and some paint fading in areas. The interior has visible wear on the upholstery and surfaces. Mechanically it runs but has some issues that may require attention. Suitable for a buyer looking for basic transportation at a reasonable price.",
